<item>
            <title>[LU-7494] sanity-hsm: lfsck repaired 207 MDT and 0 OST errors </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7494</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;andreas.dilger@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/16237&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/16237&lt;/a&gt; adds the ability to run LFSCK after each test session.  When enabled, there are repairs being reported for the filesystem that need to be investigated&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/4b297928-7588-11e5-b8f9-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/4b297928-7588-11e5-b8f9-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;11:01:38:== sanity-hsm test complete, duration 6339 sec == 11:01:38 (1445166098)
11:01:38:CMD: shadow-21vm12 /usr/sbin/lctl lfsck_start -M lustre-MDT0000 -A -t all
11:01:39:Started LFSCK on the device lustre-MDT0000: scrub layout namespace
11:01:39:CMD: shadow-21vm12 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n 			mdd.lustre-MDT0000.lfsck_layout |
11:02:10:Updated after 23s: wanted &apos;completed&apos; got &apos;completed&apos;
11:02:12: sanity-hsm : @@@@@@ FAIL: lfsck repaired 207+0 errors 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And the following test run:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/3d2990f6-7588-11e5-b8f9-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/3d2990f6-7588-11e5-b8f9-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;01:49:31:== sanityn test complete, duration 3314 sec == 01:49:30 (1445132970)
01:49:31:CMD: shadow-21vm12 /usr/sbin/lctl lfsck_start -M lustre-MDT0000 -A -t all
01:49:31:Started LFSCK on the device lustre-MDT0000: scrub layout namespace
01:49:36: sanityn : @@@@@@ FAIL: lfsck repaired 933 MDT and 0 OST errors 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
